5) Configuration and deployment constraints
- Frontend vercel rewrites route everything to index.html (single SPA host behavior).
- Backend CORS is AllowAnyOrigin/AllowAnyHeader/AllowAnyMethod (not domain-restricted currently).
- appDomain/apiBaseUrl are configurable only via environment files, but values are hardcoded in those files per build target.
- Sources:
